title: Baked Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Free Wi-fi. Catering. This coffee shop offers Vegan muffins, Vegan soup and pre-made wraps and salads with Vegan options. You get a choice of rice or soymilk for drinks and smoothies. Their green options include solar water heating and compostable take out containers.
